.TH COOLERDASH 1 "April 2026" "CoolerDash 3.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
coolerdash \- LCD temperature display for CoolerControl AIO coolers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B coolerdash
[\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]
[\fB\-\-dual\fR]
[\fB\-\-circle\fR]
[\fIconfig_path\fR]
.br
.B coolerdash
\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B coolerdash
renders real-time CPU/GPU/liquid temperatures to AIO liquid cooler LCD displays
via the CoolerControl REST API. Runs as a CoolerControl plugin managed by
.BR coolercontrold .
.PP
Two display modes:
.B dual
(CPU+GPU side-by-side) and
.B circle
(alternating single sensor). Display shape (circular/rectangular) is
auto-detected or configurable.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show usage and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose
Enable verbose logging (API calls, device detection, rendering).
.TP
.B \-\-dual
Force dual display mode. Overrides config.json.
.TP
.B \-\-circle
Force circle display mode. Overrides config.json.
.TP
.I config_path
Optional path to config.json. Default:
.IR /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/config.json .
.SH CONFIGURATION
Config file:
.IR /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/config.json .
.PP
Restart to apply changes:
.RS
.nf
.B sudo systemctl restart coolercontrold
.fi
.RE
.SS Sections
.TP
.B daemon
API address and Bearer token (\fBaccess_token\fR).
.TP
.B display
Mode, dimensions, refresh interval, brightness, orientation, shape override,
sensor slot assignment.
.TP
.B layout
Bar height/width/gap/border, label margins.
.TP
.B sensors
Temperature thresholds and color zones per sensor (cpu/gpu/liquid).
.TP
.B font
Font family and sizes.
.TP
.B colors
RGB colors for bars, borders, labels.
.PP
See
.I /usr/share/doc/coolerdash/config-guide.md
for full reference.
.SH DISPLAY SHAPE DETECTION
Auto-detection based on device and resolution:
.IP \(bu 3
NZXT Kraken ≤240×240 → rectangular (inscribe factor 1.0)
.IP \(bu 3
NZXT Kraken >240×240 → circular (inscribe factor 0.7071)
.IP \(bu 3
Unknown devices → rectangular (default)
.PP
Override in config.json:
.RS
.nf
"shape": "auto"          // auto-detect (default)
"shape": "rectangular"   // force inscribe factor 1.0
"shape": "circular"      // force inscribe factor 0.7071
.fi
.RE
.SH INSTALLATION
.SS Arch Linux
.RS
.nf
.B yay -S coolerdash-git
.B sudo systemctl restart coolercontrold
.fi
.RE
.SS From Source
.RS
.nf
.B git clone https://github.com/damachine/coolerdash.git
.B cd coolerdash
.B make install
.B sudo systemctl restart coolercontrold
.fi
.RE
.SH REQUIREMENTS
.TP
.B CoolerControl
Version >=4.x, running.
.TP
.B Architecture
x86-64-v3 (Intel Haswell+ / AMD Excavator+)
.TP
.B Dependencies
cairo, jansson, libcurl-gnutls, ttf-roboto
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
.B coolerdash --verbose
.B coolerdash --circle --verbose
.B coolerdash --dual /path/to/config.json
.B journalctl -xeu coolercontrold -f
.B curl http://localhost:11987/devices | jq
.fi
.SH TROUBLESHOOTING
.TP
.B Service won't start
Check \fBsystemctl status coolercontrold\fR.
.TP
.B No devices found
Check \fBcurl http://localhost:11987/devices\fR.
.TP
.B Content clipped on circular display
Set \fB"shape": "circular"\fR in config.json.
.TP
.B Too much padding
Set \fB"shape": "rectangular"\fR in config.json.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/config.json
Configuration file.
.TP
.I /usr/libexec/coolerdash/coolerdash
Plugin binary.
.TP
.I /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/shutdown.png
Shutdown display image (registered with CC4 at startup).
.TP
.I /etc/coolercontrol/plugins/coolerdash/coolerdash.png
Generated display image.
.TP
.I /tmp/coolerdash.pid
PID file.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success / graceful shutdown.
.TP
.B 1
Error (config, connection, device).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR systemctl (1),
.BR journalctl (1)
.PP
